project_descr: The objective of this project is to enhance the capacity of national, regional and pre-municipalities authorities and to reinforce a inclusive and participatory planning in order to improve food security and reduce poverty.

outputs.output_descr: This joint UNDP-UNCDF programme aims to create the conditions for decentralization in Guinea Bissau building on lessons learned from the PADDL project.
